        <profile name="Earthshaker Rounds" typeId="9cc3-6d83-4dd3-9b64" typeName="Abilities" hidden="false" id="d90c-f4ea-82bb-bca3">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="9b8f-694b-e5e-b573">In your Shooting phase, after this model has shot, if one or more of those attacks made with its earthshaker cannon scored a hit against an enemy **^^Infantry^^** unit, until the start of your next Shooting phase, that unit is shaken. While a unit is shaken, subtract 2&quot; from its Move characteristic and subtract 2 from Charge rolls made for it.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
